    "Subject": "Welcome to Sports Journal \ud83c\udfbe",
    "Text": "Hi {{#if name}}{{name}}{{else}}there{{/if}},\n\nWelcome to Sports Journal! We're excited to help you track every training session, competition, and milestone across your sport.\n\nStart by completing your athlete profile, then log your first performance to see insights appear instantly.\n\nNeed a hand? Reply to this email and our team will be right with you.\n\nLet's make every performance count!\nThe Sports Journal Team",
    "Html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\\n<html lang=\\\"en\\\">\\n<head>\\n  <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n  <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n  <title>Welcome to Sports Journal</title>\\n  <style>\\n    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@500;600;700&display=swap');\\n  </style>\\n</head>\\n<body style=\\\"margin:0;background-color:#f3f4f6;font-family:'Inter',Arial,sans-serif;\\\">\\n  <table role=\\\"presentation\\\" cellpadding=\\\"0\\\" cellspacing=\\\"0\\\" width=\\\"100%\\\" style=\\\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#3b82f6,#8b5cf6,#06d6a0);padding:40px 0;\\\">\\n    <tr>\\n      <td align=\\\"center\\\">\\n        <table role=\\\"presentation\\\" cellpadding=\\\"0\\\" cellspacing=\\\"0\\\" width=\\\"600\\\" style=\\\"max-width:600px;background-color:#ffffff;border-radius:24px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 20px 45px rgba(31,41,55,0.15);\\\">\\n          <tr>\\n            <td style=\\\"padding:32px 32px 0 32px;text-align:center;background-color:#0f172a;\\\">\\n              <img src=\\\"https://sportsjournal.app/lovable-uploads/008aa3aa-1776-43dd-9916-f0b8fd2a8faa.png\\\" alt=\\\"Sports Journal\\\" style=\\\"max-width:220px;width:100%;border-radius:18px;\\\" />\\n            </td>\\n          </tr>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td style=\\\"padding:32px 36px 28px 36px;color:#0f172a;\\\">\\n              <h1 style=\\\"margin:0 0 16px;font-size:28px;color:#1f2937;\\\">Welcome to Sports Journal, {{#if name}}{{name}}{{else}}Athlete{{/if}}!</h1>\\n              <p style=\\\"margin:0 0 20px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#4b5563;\\\">We're thrilled to have you training with us. Sports Journal is your home for logging performances, monitoring progress, and staying motivated across every individual sport.</p>\\n              <table role=\\\"presentation\\\" cellpadding=\\\"0\\\" cellspacing=\\\"0\\\" width=\\\"100%\\\" style=\\\"margin:24px 0;background:#f9fafb;border-radius:16px;padding:24px;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;\\\">\\n                <tr>\\n                  <td style=\\\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#374151;\\\">\\n                    <strong style=\\\"display:block;margin-bottom:12px;color:#2563eb;font-size:16px;\\\">Quick start guide</strong>\\n                    <ol style=\\\"margin:0;padding-left:20px;\\\">\\n                      <li style=\\\"margin-bottom:12px;\\\"><strong>Complete your profile:</strong> Share your sport, focus areas, and goals so insights stay personal.</li>\\n                      <li style=\\\"margin-bottom:12px;\\\"><strong>Log your first performance:</strong> Record a training session or event to unlock trends on your dashboard instantly.</li>\\n                      <li><strong>Reflect consistently:</strong> Add notes after each effort and watch improvement shine through season-long analytics.</li>\\n                    </ol>\\n                  </td>\\n                </tr>\\n              </table>\\n              <table role=\\\"presentation\\\" cellpadding=\\\"0\\\" cellspacing=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"margin:0 0 24px;\\\">\\n                <tr>\\n                  <td>\\n                    <a href=\\\"https://sportsjournal.app\\\" style=\\\"display:inline-block;padding:14px 28px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#3b82f6,#8b5cf6);color:#ffffff;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;border-radius:999px;box-shadow:0 12px 25px rgba(79,70,229,0.45);\\\">Open Sports Journal</a>\\n                  </td>\\n                </tr>\\n              </table>\\n              <p style=\\\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:15px;color:#4b5563;\\\">Questions or feedback? Just reply to this email\u2014we read every message.</p>\\n              <p style=\\\"margin:0;font-size:15px;color:#4b5563;\\\">Let's make every performance count.<br />The Sports Journal Team</p>\\n            </td>\\n          </tr>\\n          <tr>\\n            <td style=\\\"padding:20px 36px 32px;text-align:center;background-color:#0f172a;color:#d1d5db;font-size:13px;\\\">\\n              <p style=\\\"margin:0 0 8px;\\\">Follow your progress. Embrace the grind.</p>\\n              <a href=\\\"https://sportsjournal.app\\\" style=\\\"color:#06d6a0;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;\\\">sportsjournal.app</a>\\n            </td>\\n          </tr>\\n        </table>\\n      </td>\\n    </tr>\\n  </table>\\n</body>\\n</html>"
  }
